Subject: [PATCH V6 02/20] uapi: always define F_GETLK64/F_SETLK64/F_SETLKW64 in fcntl.h
Date:   Thu, 24 Feb 2022 16:53:52 +0800
Message-Id: <20220224085410.399351-3-guoren@kernel.org>
